ranular grain\nboundary sliding and transgranular phase transformation. Furthermore, an\ninverse Hall-Petch relationship is revealed describing the correlation between\ngrain size and strength for polycrystalline YSTZ nanopillars with grain sizes\nbelow 15 nm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Dec 2018 18:06:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-05-02"}
