tion between star\nformation history or specific star formation rate and halo formation time is\nconsistent with being weak.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Dec 2018 20:07:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jul 2020 21:05:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-09"}
